name: MemberTrack
short: Uses RedBots storage to track how long a member has been in the server.
description: Uses RedBots storage to track memebers join date and assign roles based on time spent in the server..
end_user_data_statement: This cog stores End User Data when storing the items of a user. If a user requests data-deletion, all their data will be removed from the bot.
install_msg: Thanks for installing MemberTrack. Load the cog with `[p]load membertrack` and see all its commands with `[p]help MemberTrack`
author: elkz
